data.title: Summer Concert Series at Center Memorial Park
data.meta_description: Bring your lawn chairs and picnic dinner or take out from one of our fabulous Downtown restaurants.
data.text:
The August 8th concert will be held at the Rain Location: Army Navy Club.

Bring your lawn chair and dinner or take out from one of Downtown’s great restaurants. Rain location: Army Navy Club 1090 Main St., Downtown Manchester. Sponsored by Beller’s Music in association with DMSSD, Arts & Culture Commission, and the Department of Leisure, Family, and Recreation.
